<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>About Church</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0b1220,#111827);
    color:white;
}

/* NAV */
nav{
    padding:15px 30px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    background:rgba(15,23,42,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin:0 10px;
    font-size:14px;
}

nav a:hover{
    color:#38bdf8;
}

/* HEADER */
.header{
    text-align:center;
    padding:60px 20px;
}

.header h1{
    font-size:40px;
    color:#38bdf8;
}

.header p{
    opacity:0.7;
    margin-top:10px;
}

/* GRID */
.container{
    max-width:1000px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:20px;
}

.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}

/* CARD */
.card{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:15px;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-5px);
    border-color:#38bdf8;
}

/* ICON STYLE */
.icon{
    font-size:30px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    font-size:13px;
    opacity:0.6;
    margin-top:40px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
<div><b>Grace Church</b></div>
<div>
<a href="index.html">Home</a>
<a href="about.html">About</a>
<a href="sermons.html">Sermons</a>
<a href="events.html">Events</a>
<a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
</div>
</nav>

<div class="header">
<h1>About Us</h1>
<p>Discover our mission, vision and values</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<div class="icon">🎯</div>
<h3>Our Mission</h3>
<p>To spread the gospel of Jesus Christ and build strong believers through teaching and prayer.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="icon">🌍</div>
<h3>Our Vision</h3>
<p>To create a global spiritual community rooted in love, unity, and faith in God.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="icon">❤️</div>
<h3>Our Values</h3>
<p>Love, faith, prayer, humility, and service to others.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="icon">🙏</div>
<h3>Our Belief</h3>
<p>We believe in God the Father, Son, and Holy Spirit, and salvation through Jesus Christ.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Grace Church | About Page
</footer>

</body>
</html>
